.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, jazz, techno, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, golf, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the fan of rock is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
4. the fan of jazz is the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the fan of techno is between the fan of metal and the fan of jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | techno           | metal | rock  |
| Sport         | tennis | volleyball | golf   | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, disco, reggae, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, van, scooter
1. the fan of disco is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of classical##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of classical is between the person driving the helicopter and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | disco | classical | reggae      |
| Transport     | van | helicopter    | airplane  | scooter |

