.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cricket, sailing, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, boat, skateboard
1. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the boat##2
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | baseball | snowboarding | sailing     | cricket   |
| Transport   | boat   | quad-bike     | skateboard | bus |

