.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, chef, social-worker, analyst
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, motorbike, subway
1. the social-worker is between the person driving the trike and the bartender##2
2. the person driving the subway is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the analyst is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
5. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | chef | social-worker | bartender | analyst |
| Transport   | trike         | subway       | quad-bike    | motorbike         |

