.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, cranberry, grapes, kiwi
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo, rowing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
3. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person eating cranberry and the person who's sport is cricket##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | kiwi   | grapes      | cranberry   | radish  |
| Sport   | cricket | water-polo | rowing | lacrosse |

