.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, garlic, mango, watermelon
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, disaster, zombie, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person eating garlic is between the person eating watermelon and the person eating spinach##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | spinach     | garlic | watermelon   | mango        |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie   | disaster | spy |

