.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, camping, traveling, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, blues, electronic, rock
1. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of indie is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the fan of blues##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the fan of blues is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | traveling | skydiving | sudoku |
| Music-Genre   | electronic          | blues     | rock  | indie     |

