4. the analyst is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | analyst | chef | dancer | software-developer     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | spy    | epic   | satire |

