2. the indonesian is the person driving the ship##1
3. the australian is between the person driving the ship and the spanish##2
4. the indonesian is on the right of the australian##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | polish | spanish | australian | indonesian |
| Transport     | tram     | trike   | jet-ski | ship  |

