.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, malaysian, dutch, indian
4 different pets are kept: rat, frog, bird, fish
1. the nigerian is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
2. the indian is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the malaysian##2
4. the owner of the fish is the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | indian | malaysian | nigerian | dutch |
| Pet           | bird  | fish  | frog | rat      |

