2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the italian is the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is between the mexican and the turkish##2
5. the turkish is the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian   | mexican   | dutch | turkish |
| Sport         | parkour | rugby | climbing     | volleyball    |

