.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, reading, cooking
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, dog, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | reading    | cooking     | video-games | puzzles |
| Pet     | horse | snake | dog       | hedgehog     |

 